@startuml sequence_build_pdf
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Build PDF Resume

actor "Job Seeker" as User
participant "build-pdf.mjs" as Script
participant "templates/resume.html" as Template
participant "Playwright\n(Chromium)" as Browser
participant "exports/" as Output

User -> Script : node build-pdf.mjs <path>
Script -> Script : Read and parse\nMarkdown to HTML fragment
Script -> Template : Read HTML template
Template --> Script : Returns HTML wrapper
Script -> Script : Inject HTML fragment\ninto template
Script -> Browser : Launch headless Chromium\nLoad merged HTML page
Browser --> Script : Page rendered
Script -> Browser : page.pdf() — export to PDF
Browser --> Script : PDF buffer
Script -> Output : Write <basename>.pdf
Output --> User : PDF ready in exports/

@enduml
